T01TD1117E:63a-0: @63a ` // bdud btul ba la bstod pa bzhugs /
T01TD1117E:63a-2: # // dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1117E:63b-0: bsam gtan phyin ci log gis ci zhig dgongs mdzad skad cig @63b legs par spyan dbye gzigs //
T01TD1117E:63b-1: lus med mda' yis gzir ba'i skye bo bdag cag skyob pas kyang ni bsrung bar mi mdzad na //
T01TD1117E:63b-2: thugs rje ldan pa phyin ci log gyur khyod las mchog tu ma rung skyes bu gzhan ma mchis //
T01TD1117E:63b-3: phrag dog ldan pa bdud kyi bud med de skad smra yang rgyal ba skyob pa byang chub gyur //
T01TD1117E:63b-4: gzhan yang 'dod dbang gis ni kun du gzhu bkang bdud gzhan lag par myur pa pa ta ha sgra 'jebs dang ldan //
T01TD1117E:63b-5: dpa' bo smin ma bskyod dang nyer g-yo lta bur sgeg dang 'dzum dang rol pa med rnams kyis //
T01TD1117E:63b-6: thub dbang skyob pa byang chub ma brnyes par du bsam gtan las ni bskyod ma nus pa mthong gyur nas //
T01TD1117E:63b-7: ngo mtshar gyur pas pa spu langs pa'i lus kyis grub pa rnams dang yan lag mchog rnams 'dud //
T01TD1117E:63b-8: ral pa 'khrugs shing lce rnams g-yogs la kun du bltams pas gang gi thugs rnams 'khrul par ma gyur cing //
T01TD1117E:63b-9: rab gsal 'dod lha'i bdud rnams rtse mo mchog dag lag thogs glang po rta rnams gdong ldan seng ge dang //
T01TD1117E:63b-10: stag gi gdong rnams rtsva bzhin grangs med gyur pa 'khor ba yis ni gang zhig bsnyengs par ma gyur pa //
T01TD1117E:63b-11: de ni kun la gnod pa'i rnam pa 'dres pa med par skyob pa sangs rgyas thub dbang 'jig rten mgon //
T01TD1117E:63b-12: bdud btul ba la bstod pa /
T01TD1117E:63b-13: rab dga'i lha'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
